# Telegram (manual payment verification)
# 1) Create a bot via @BotFather and set TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
# 2) Set a webhook secret (any random string) and register the webhook with Telegram
#    so Telegram includes `X-Telegram-Bot-Api-Secret-Token` on every webhook call.
# 3) Add your admin chat IDs (comma-separated) so only you can approve/reject.
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_SECRET_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_ADMIN_CHAT_IDS=
